Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:01:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Against Perfect Machine King's unfathomable Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otogi-{\i0}kun{\i1} and Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1} thought it was all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after hearing\N Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1} used the power of the card Honda-{\i0}kun{\i1} left for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was able\N to beat the Big Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet, Honda-{\i0}kun{\i1} still\N didn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kidnapped Mokuba:\N Kaiba VS Psycho Shocker"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Everything seems bigger for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys said their goal was to get our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0} hasn't disappeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be around\N here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I have a huge\N grudge against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking's pointless!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! So you're safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here to get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right,\N I'm one of the Big Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soichiro Ota!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This body now belongs to {\i1}me{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you underestimate my grade 5 kendo skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! You went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I'll be taking the thing you care most about with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ota! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... Did Honda really\N get his ass taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the thing from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's with this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this poor thing's been captured and turned into a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy could be\N leading you into a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly possible,\N considering the world we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's dangerous,\N we should probably break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This little guy\N could be trying to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he tried to save Kaiba-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I {\i1}guess{\i0} that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Shizuka-chan insists on it,\N we'll spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, let's follow Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man inside Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0} should know where the real one's being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! If ya don't settle down, I'm seriously beat ya to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just hang on, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite some time, Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you {\i1}forgotten{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you bring it up, I saw a man holding a kid drive past here a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ota, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... this is to pay Kaiba back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I told you to refrain from using cheap methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't act now, I'll never get another opportunity to get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking pretty pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} will watch over the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}disobeying{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you'd do something as low as taking Mokuba hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more naive than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} was the one who {\i1}saved{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring my brother\N here this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on,\N your big brother will begin his Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's going to Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire to go to where Mokuba is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are going to have to {\i1}defeat me{\i0} first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you\N stand a change against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble your deck, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no matter how hard you look, you won't find the God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are forbidden cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done building your deck, choose your Deck Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my Deck Master, I choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord of Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to tell you, but I think it'd be funner for you to anticipate it later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will make the shock that much greater for you later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An obvious bluff won't work against {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blue flame burns deep within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't afraid of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then place\N two more cards face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Spear Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spear Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it attacks a Monster whose Attack Power is lower than its Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this card gives damage to the player as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you keep a Wall Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Spear Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Screw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the Demon Scout you destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my opponent is forced to draw three cards, and if there are any Magic Cards among them, it must be discarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, toss aside any Magic Cards you are holding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can still play a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My set card is\N the Deck Destruction Virus of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this match is as good as over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this timing\N to activate my Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing of God is a card that increases my Life Points by 500 every time I draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of this card's effect, I will increase my Life Points by 500 right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Daimon, your deck will only live for one more turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And next turn, I'll give you heavy damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a Monster Card in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then place one card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spear Dragon is a Monster that automatically switches to Defense Mode after dealing battle damage to the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it has 0 Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even knowing that, he won't attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, come {\b0}attack{\b1} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no idea what you're planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you're finished this very instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Giant Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I switch Spear Dragon\N into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Dragon, attack his Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask of Perplexity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask of Perplexity blinds you and causes you to be unable to see where you are attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a card that lets me\N switch the attack target!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you won't be able to tell who you are attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Dragon, attack him over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just ordered Spear Dragon to attack {\i1}your{\i0} Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Daimon, {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who's been trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use Giant Germ as the needed sacrifice to activate my Trap Card, Deck Destruction Virus of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was my Trap Card destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Deck Master...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master Ability holds the power to block all of my opponent's Traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba, you will {\i1}never{\i0} be activating Trap Cards {\i1}again{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sold many Kaiba Corporation missiles and other weapons of war to other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the most popular was the virtual system {\i1}you{\i0} created.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, the program you invented is being used around the world as a mean of combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...forced Gozaburo Kaiba to his death", am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gozaburo's first mistake was giving you a birthday present that would eventually lead to his doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beginning today, Seto, your format education will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me take this\N opportunity to praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today is your birthday.\N I have a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto, Mokuba... As of today, you each hold two percent of Kaiba Corporation's stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am going to loan you this money, with the condition that you must pay it all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Loan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Starting right now, your year-long test will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must return 100 times that money within that time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you cannot accomplish something as small as this, you have no hopes of ever running Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now sign this IOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or would you like to return to your {\b0}previous{\b1} home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will have Daimon lend his aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with that, I'll be looking forward to our meeting in one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, what are you\N going to do, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Paying back the money 100-fold is way too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Relax. This is simply a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've got 100 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This card represents one percent of the total stocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, it's a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a rule among stock marketers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person who holds this card cannot be bought out by any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever holds the\N card can't be bought out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meaning it makes 51%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If a person holds at least\N 51 of the total 100 cards,\N no other person will have anything higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You win the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Daimon, use all of the money to purchase 51% of the stocks of any company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You want to spend it all right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any company will do, so long as it is highly rated and traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto-{\i0}sama{\i1}, I have successfully purchased a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have selected an old funeral home in which the workers are highly devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awesome! So that makes you the president of this company, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Becoming the president of such a small business will not serve my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be impossible to earn 100 times the price in just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there is a way to make them pay it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You intend for me to buy my company back at five times the price?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't, I will fire both you and your employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be a huge loss for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe such a young boy could think up a plan so evil...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability to earn money far surpassed Gozaburo's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:16:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gozaburo used the virtual system I invented for military weapons, crushing my dream in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided then in my heart that I would do all it took to use that man and {\i1}surpass{\i0} him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all of that ends\N right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream will perish along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Effect of Giant Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon the same card\N from my deck onto the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, thanks to the year I spent by your side, I've learned quite a bit about you and your territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without Traps at your disposal, you can only use the power of your Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe in my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Blessing of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regain 500 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then place two cards face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Dragon, attack his Wall Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Screw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Effect of Cyber Pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Monsters on the field are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And both players\N draw five cards from their deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then Summon any {\s1}Level 4{\s0} Monster Card you hold on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're at a draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Blessing of God, I regain 500 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then use a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Tranquilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This device were designed by Gozaburo himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was intended to be a new weapon developed by Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we give it a little test?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Tranquilizer is a Magic Card that drains an opponent's Monster 100 Attack Points times their level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the Level 4 Blood Vorse's Attack Power will go down 400 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he only has a 500 Attack Power Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will also activate the Special Effect of Injection Angel Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By paying 1000 of my Life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can raise Lilly's Attack Points by 3000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has 3400 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to diagnose\N the Seto Kaiba disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebek's Blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebek's Blessing is a card that increases my Life by the amount of damage my opponent received.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:19:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brings me another step towards victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lilly's Attack Power has returned to 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Worm Beast has 1400 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I get through, I can heavily wound his Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he uses Lilly's Effect again to raise her Attack Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take the hit instead and my Life will drop to 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just have to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've endured countless problems in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll place a Monster in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not going to attack...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll activate another Trap before it shifts to your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Absorbing Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Life Absorbing Machine is a card that returns half of the Life Points you lost in your previous turn once per turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he's setting up a Life Recovery Combo so he can use Lilly endlessly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the effect of Blessing of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regain some of my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll let you see it, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest weapon Gozaburo ever built!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sacrifice both Defense Monsters I have on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to Summon {\i1}this{\i0} Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long this road goes on for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's netter if we don't run into any other roads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way we won't lose sight of our-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, look at that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world {\i1}is{\i0} that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Psycho Shocker as his Deck Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} can't use any Trap Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to Imperial Command of the Royal Palace, even all his Magic Cards have been sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With no hopes of winning the Duel in site,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Satellite Cannon targets Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way for Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} to fight this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Attack from Space: Satellite Cannon"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
